name: Heathrow Natural Food and Beverage
overview: Heathrow Natural Food & Beverage, Inc. distributes natural food products in the United States. It principally offers Exfuze, a nutritional beverage. The company also markets various nutritional products, such as chewing gums, dry bars, snack foods, and breakfast items. In addition, it produces the WGL Million Dollar Shootout reality television series. Heathrow Natural Food & Beverage, Inc. sells its products through independent distributors, Internet, and call centers. The company was formerly known as WGL Entertainment Holdings, Inc. and changed its name to Heathrow Natural Food & Beverage, Inc. in March 2009. Heathrow Natural Food & Beverage, Inc. was incorporated in 1998 and is based in Lake Mary, Florida.
